s.text: The past slips into you finally.Generations kept these secrets.Islands fell asleep looking at the sea.The one who ruled you above will rule youbelow, taking you down to show you the cut part of the wheat.Probably she was earth, your hunger was beautiful,her hunger was beautiful,but what do you really know?
